## Clonando em Nova MÃ¡quina

### Modo Aberto (submodule)

Se vocÃª clonar um projeto que jÃ¡ tem os submodules:

```bash
git clone --recursive https://github.com/seu/projeto.git
# ou
git clone https://github.com/seu/projeto.git
cd projeto
git submodule update --init --recursive
```

### Modo Stealth (clone)

Se o projeto usa modo stealth, rodar o script de setup:

```bash
# Exemplo:
git clone -b main https://github.com/pdmartins/.copilot-core.git .copilot-core
git clone -b {branch} https://github.com/pdmartins/.copilot-project.git .copilot-project
mkdir -p .github/instructions
ln -s ../../.copilot-core/instructions/agent-skills-core.instructions.md .github/instructions/agent-skills-core.instructions.md
ln -s ../../.copilot-project/instructions/agent-skills-project.instructions.md .github/instructions/agent-skills-project.instructions.md
```

