## Troubleshooting

### "fatal: repository not found"
Verifique se tem acesso aos repositÃ³rios via `git clone`.

### "submodule already exists"
Remova e refaÃ§a:
```bash
git rm --cached .copilot-core .copilot-project
rm -rf .copilot-core .copilot-project
```

### Submodules nÃ£o aparecem apÃ³s clone
```bash
git submodule update --init --recursive
```

